resources.string:
Select either raw sensor readings or interpolated data. 

Selecting raw sensor readings enables: 
• how several readings in the same grid cell are aggregated; 
• whether to focus on data collected next to a bus line or not; 
• the grid size (in meters). 

The interpolated data are pre computed maps that use all sensor readings to compute a map that covers the region of Lisbon. These maps are computed on a hourly basis.
